《'''挂在外面的情人'''》（''Well Hung Lover''）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://faureforart.eklablog.com/naked-man-a130109592|title=Naked Man|date=2017-05-08|website=Fauré for Art|access-date=2018-01-13|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729102918/http://faureforart.eklablog.com/naked-man-a130109592|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/bristol/5193552.stm|title='Naked man' mural allowed to stay|date=2006-07-19|website=BBC News|access-date=2018-01-24|archive-date=2009-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211124033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/bristol/5193552.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一幅由匿名街头艺术家[[班克斯|班克斯]]创作的壁画，位于英格兰[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]弗罗格莫尔街布鲁克性病诊所（已搬迁）侧面的墙上<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/art/art-news/10011866/Banksy-mural-encroached-on-by-rival-street-artist.html|title=Banksy mural encroached on by rival street artist|date=2013-04-23|access-date=2017-01-27|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922234347/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/art/art-news/10011866/Banksy-mural-encroached-on-by-rival-street-artist.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，绘于2006年。壁画距离地面高约5米，而[[公园街_(布里斯托尔)|公园街]]跨越弗罗格莫尔街的高架桥上几乎与其平齐，因此是最好的观赏壁画的地点<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://visitbristol.co.uk/things-to-do/banksy-grafitti-well-hung-lover-p1870753|title=Banksy Grafitti [sic] Well-Hung Lover|website=Visit Bristol|access-date=2018-01-09|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026220651/https://visitbristol.co.uk/things-to-do/banksy-grafitti-well-hung-lover-p1870753|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是英国第一件合法的街头艺术品，获得了布里斯托市议会的追溯许可和保护。
[[File:Bridge_over_Frogmore_Street_-_geograph.org.uk_-_200561.jpg|thumb]]
壁画描绘了一个裸体男子挂在窗外，右臂挂在窗台上，左臂遮盖生殖器；窗内有两个人：衣着整齐的丈夫向窗外寻找，旁边是仅穿内衣的妻子<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.complex.com/style/greatest-banksy-artwork/|title=The Greatest Banksy Artwork of All Time|last=Lynch|first=Sean|date=2018-09-08|website=Complex|access-date=2018-01-09|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226203016/https://www.complex.com/style/greatest-banksy-artwork/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=http://calliglyphs.blogspot.co.uk/2015/03/banksy-graffiti-and-blue-paint.html?m=1|title=Banksy, Graffiti and Blue Paint Calliglyphs - the Naked Hanging Man|last=Daniell|first=Chris|date=2015-03-01|website=Calliglyphs, Graffiti and Other Marginalia of the World|access-date=2018-01-09|archive-date=2018-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216025436/http://calliglyphs.blogspot.co.uk/2015/03/banksy-graffiti-and-blue-paint.html?m=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==历史==
[[File:Affair.JPG|thumb]]
壁画创作过程中，为了达到适当的高度，并保持壁画的秘密，在墙上架设了脚手架，并用防水布遮盖。<ref name=":3" />三天后，委员会拆除了脚手架，露出了艺术品。

《挂在外面的情人》出现时，市议会的政策还是打击涂鸦，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://amp.theguardian.com/uk/2006/sep/17/arts.artsnews1|title=Banksy- Britain: lover hanging on a window sill|date=2006-09-17|website=The Guardian|access-date=2018-01-19|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729112636/https://amp.theguardian.com/uk/2006/sep/17/arts.artsnews1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 因此议会最初是反对这幅壁画。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/elusive-street-artist-banksy-source-pride-british-town-article-1.1485180|title=Elusive street artist Banksy a source of pride for one British town|last=Moran|first=Lee|date=2013-10-15|website=New York Daily News|access-date=2018-01-24|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729104014/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/elusive-street-artist-banksy-source-pride-british-town-article-1.1485180|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，一些居民支持这幅作品，说它"照亮了"这个地区。<ref name=":1" /> 市议会面临要求保留壁画的压力，举行了一项在线民意调查，询问是否应该保留壁画。97%的受访者支持该壁画，<ref name=":1" /> 从而获得了英国第一幅合法的街头艺术壁画的追溯许可。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/uk/bristol-street-art-class-tour-banksy-graffiti-where-the-wall-a7980326.html|title=Bristol street art class lets you make believe you're Banksy|last=Dening|first=Lizzy|date=2017-01-24|website=The Independent|access-date=2018-01-24|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729143728/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/uk/bristol-street-art-class-tour-banksy-graffiti-where-the-wall-a7980326.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 市议会强调，这是一个例外，未来的街头艺术不一定被容忍。<ref name=":1" />

2009年，壁画被彩弹枪玷污，随后市议会部分修复。2018年第二次被涂上黑色喷漆。

2020年，《挂在外面的情人》被纳入一组新的艺术品，称为"邻居"。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bristol247.com/culture/art/city-centre-sights-lit-up-as-bristol-light-festival-begins/|title=CITY CENTRE SIGHTS LIT UP AS BRISTOL LIGHT FESTIVAL BEGINS|last=Booth|first=Martin|date=27 February 2020|work=Bristol24/7|accessdate=13 September 2020|archive-date=2020-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316162058/https://www.bristol247.com/culture/art/city-centre-sights-lit-up-as-bristol-light-festival-begins/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

